5177b9a83b27124176d01d2a0213120916af0c3ebb5037990a860199aa5c41baed7d3e2876e1e7e94c4b2eb22a9f9f01bd152e454acbef8bbffad013debd65df  musl-32bit-stat-workaround.patch
"
